resources: If you could get a free trip, where would you go now and why? If you could not work in any intellectual field, what non-intellectual job would you choose? What physical accomplishment are you most proud of? If you were to work in academia in the future, what position would you hold? What do you consider to be your worst human trait? What is a movie/series that is very popular but you have not seen? Why? Which film is a must-see for you? What hobby do you wish you had more time for? Which family member are you closest to? If you could have one superpower, what would it be? What languages do you speak and want to learn? What rule do you break often? If you could live in any historical era, which would you choose? If you could live in the world of a fantasy novel, which would you choose? Would you like to be famous? How? What would you consider to be a "perfect" weekday? Tell me three things that you and your partner seem to have in common! What are you most grateful for in life? If you could change one thing about the way you were raised, what would you change? Tell your partner the story of your life in four minutes, in as much detail as you can! If you could learn the truth about yourself, your life, your future or anything else you'd like to know from a crystal ball Is there something you've been dreaming of doing for a long time? Why haven't you done it yet? What is the greatest achievement of your life? What is the greatest value to you in a friendship? What is your best memory of this summer? If you knew now that you were going to die in a year, would you change anything in your life? Why? What does friendship mean to you? What role do love and emotions play in your life? How close and intimate is your relationship with your family? Do you think you had a happier childhood than most people? Complete the sentence "I wish I had someone to share..."! If you were to become a close friend of your partner, tell me what they would need to know about you! When was the last time someone saw you cry? And when was the last time you cried alone? What is something so serious that it shouldn't be made fun of, if there are such things? Your house is on fire and all your possessions in it. You've already rescued your loved ones and pets, but the only thing you can rush back to do is rescue them. What is it? Why? How old would you be if you could choose your age now? What would you do with the rest of your life if you didn't have to work now? What did you want to be ten years ago? How close is this to your current profession? If you could do whatever you wanted for a year, what would you do? Do you have a secret talent for something, like singing? If you could choose your own first name, what would it be? What was the bravest thing you ever did? What bad qualities did you inherit from your parents? What was the best advice you ever got? What do you want to achieve in the future? What would you never want to give up in your life? What type of people do you like? What subjects or topics are you not comfortable with (why?)? What kind of music do you like? Do you have a motto, a story that has stuck with you, that you try to live by, act by? What is one thing you would change in the country? Politics, other...? How would you rob a bank? Give me a guess what a cheesecake in a hat looks like. Would you rather fight a duck the size of a horse, or a horse the size of 100 ducks? How would you start a cult? How many close friends do you have? Do you go on holiday with your friends or with your family? Why did you choose university over an OKJ course? Would you like to move abroad? If so, where? What is the next thing you would like to achieve in your life? Where would you like to be in five years? What do you think makes a friendship work? What is important to you in a friendship? What's the best productivity tip you've ever heard? Do you procrastinate, if so why? Is there a hobby/project you've wanted to do for a long time but haven't? What languages do you speak, what do you like about them? Do you use AI for work or hobbies?
